{"title":"植树节和我","authors":["张小红"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":5,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"植树节和我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张小红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满了一页一页日历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，和肩上的闪亮的铁锹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起穿过雨，穿过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在心头打上了印记的小树林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（呵！雨填满深深的脚印）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我带来又一批小树苗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"循着一个全新的诱惑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向春雷回响的前方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"植树节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我充满活力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，我准备以牺牲者的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒向每一个坑洼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（为小树苗作底肥）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒向雨后的赤亮太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把经验注入根。并且"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把思索的钢针挂满落叶松"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（或者化为雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润湿所有的年轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次又一次，都有新绿泛出）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培土吧，大地由于种下了树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（不，种下了我）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——将更加充满生气新"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}